MICHAEL (OFFSCREEN): How does
it feel that you were the

45:49.848 --> 45:52.083
director of the worst
movie ever made?

45:52.117 --> 45:55.053
-I feel I didn't do
the worst movie.

45:55.086 --> 45:57.422
I did a very good movie.

45:57.455 --> 46:03.929
If they all say, worst
movie, ah, them

46:03.962 --> 46:05.563
problem, not my problem.

46:05.596 --> 46:08.967
My problem is to shoot
a lot of movies.

46:09.000 --> 46:10.869
I want to shoot a
lot of movies.

46:10.902 --> 46:11.970
I can't--

46:12.003 --> 46:13.171
I can't stop.

